data.description: This beautifully designed home features 200 feet of private dock and stunning views of the Peace River. Located in the Harbor Heights community, this exceptional waterfront residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. It's situated at the end of a peaceful coastal community, offering fabulous panoramic views of the Peace River and its spectacular sunsets. Oversized corner lot. This charming dream home has ceramic tile floors and a central island kitchen. You'll appreciate the upgraded stainless steel vent stack over the stove, the glass tile backsplash, built-in microwave, and the kitchen sink with a view of the canal. The lovely great room and dining area showcase laminated floors, custom valances, and an upgraded paddle fan. Enjoy canal-side dinners with views from the dining room window! The wonderful master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and sliding doors leading to the air-conditioned office with a complete ocean view. The fully renovated master bathroom offers a tiled shower with a rain-type fixed showerhead and an additional private toilet space. Two of the guest bedrooms have private bathrooms. The third bedroom has an independent entrance, perfect for visitors. The house is adorned with built-in cabinets and custom valances. The laundry room includes a washer/dryer and spacious built-in shelves. Additionally, there's a large pantry. This beautiful property requires minimal exterior maintenance. Designed with a private terrace where you can relax to the soothing sound of the private Koi pond waterfall, or enjoy a delightful dinner on the lower patio terrace by the canal while admiring the breathtaking view. This property is an ideal dream for fishing enthusiasts, water sports lovers, and outdoor activities. The property includes two built-in sheds for additional storage. If you're a nature lover, seeking spectacular views and enthusiastic about boating, this home is perfect for you. It's located just minutes from downtown Punta Gorda, where you can enjoy shopping and exquisite restaurants, with easy access to I-75 and proximity to schools and churches. You can't afford to miss this opportunity!
